      "name": "Eclepsis, Dragon Ruler of Woes",
      "effect": "2 Level 7 Dragon monsters\nIf this card is Xyz Summoned: You can target 1 Level 4 or lower \"Dragon Ruler\" monster in your GY or banishment; Special Summon 1 Level/Rank 7 \"Dragon Ruler\" monster mentioned on it from your Deck or banishment, then shuffle that target into the Deck. When your opponent activates a Spell/Trap Card or effect (Quick Effect): You can detach 2 materials from this card; negate the activation, and if you do, banish that card. You can only use each effect of \"Eclepsis, Dragon Ruler of Woes\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
